# Parfumbox — Project

pnpm monorepo with three apps:

- `apps/api` — NestJS + Prisma + MinIO
- `apps/web` — Telegram Mini App (Vite + React + RTK Query)
- `apps/admin` — Admin panel (Vite + React + Mantine)

## Golden rules

- Never edit `dist/`, `node_modules/`, `coverage/`, or `pnpm-lock.yaml` by hand.
- Never commit secrets (bot token, JWT secrets, MinIO keys).
- Prefer `pnpm --filter <app> <script>` over `cd apps/x && npm …`.
- Read architecture docs before large changes:
  - `docs/BACKEND_ARCHITECTURE.md`
  - `docs/FRONTEND_ARCHITECTURE.md`
  - `docs/DEVOPS.md`
  - `docs/PRODUCT_ARCHITECTURE.md`

## API domains

One folder per domain under `apps/api/src/` (e.g. `auth/`, `products/`, `orders/`, `cart/`). Admin routes live under `admin-*` modules with separate JWT guards.
